is now 23 years old. He was born in a military landlord family in Fengshan County, Liaoyang, Da Zhou. His father died of a recurrence of knife wounds when he was ten years old, leaving only his mother Cui.



At the age of 14, he joined the army and was selected into the Zhaowu Camp of the Ban Army. He became the chief auxiliary officer of the big week, Hongyuan Qinjun.



Due to the suppression of Yong Liang party item uprising, meritocratic promotion to Xuanwu Ban Army is seven product command, commander of a battalion of more than 1,000 people.
